snippet.title: Cheeky Chickens 2
snippet.description:
http://loadupgames.com/cheeky-chickens-2/

90 FUN LEVELS of pig-popping pleasure!

The Cheeky Chickens are back in an all new sequel - The yolk's on you!


- 6 Cheeky Episodes.
- 90 Challenging Levels.
- HD Graphics.
- Funny Sound Effects.
- Gamepad Support for PC, Mac, Linux and Consoles.
- Red Bird, Little Bird, Little Female Bird, Big Bird, Bird Dropper, Big Female Bird, and Penguin Bird.
- Pork Ready to be Plated.


It's Addictive and Loads of Fun! Good Luck!
